              <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
              <decoNote type="miniature"><locus n="44v"/>The Mongols leaving the <name type="place">valley of Irgene Kun</name> where they had taken refuge for 400 years from the Tatars.</decoNote>
              <decoNote type="miniature"><locus n="49v"/><name key="http://lccn.loc.gov/n82024842" type="person">Ching&#x12B;z Kh&#x101;n</name> fighting the Chinese in the mountains.</decoNote>
