              <decoNote type="miniature"><locus n="89v"/>The Caliph, <name key="http://lccn.loc.gov/no2006103855" type="person">al-Musta'&#x1E63;im</name>, brought before <name type="person">H&#x16B;l&#x101;g&#x16B; Kh&#x101;n</name>.</decoNote>
